title: Boyega escapes Atlanta snow, makes ‘Last Jedi’ premiere

og.title: Boyega escapes Atlanta snow, makes 'Last Jedi' premiere
og.description: After tweeting that snow in Atlanta might keep him from making the "Star Wars: The Last Jedi" premiere in Los Angeles, actor John Boyega made it to the red carpet _ and no starship was required.
